data.description: Step into the warmth of open spaces with volume ceilings & generous spaces where luxury meets comfort. Enjoy the perfect backyard oasis with a covered porch, fenced yard, & your own private pool for soaking in the sun. The stylish kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, plenty of counter space for prepping meals & a breakfast nook. Indulge in custom closets and a master bath with his and hers vanities. Community perks include basketball, tennis courts, fitness room, & the heartwarming embrace of a close-knit neighborhood. Your new home is a haven where elegance & community unite seamlessly.
